PUBLB7.original: Great weed. Lumberjacks. A shitty military. Canada is beginning to look better every day for those of us who want to live a peaceful life composting our own shit, drinking fair trade coffee and preaching to everyone about the evils of plastic. With the passing of the US Jingoism Act, it is clear that many Americans are not welcome anymore. The founders of our country were noble men who, upon losing their teeth, did like George Washington and had new ones extracted from their slaves and implanted into their own. It's that kind of freedom that this country was founded on - freedom for some, tough luck for the rest. We're liberal, and it's our time to be on top next.
PUBLB7.translated: 优质大麻、伐木工人、垃圾军队。对于我们中想要平静生活的人来说，加拿大的魅力与日俱增，你可以将自己的粪便用于施肥，喝公平贸易咖啡，向别人宣扬塑料的罪恶。在美国沙文主义法案通过后，显然会有许多人被「开除美籍」。我们国家的创立者都是贵族，在失去牙齿后，他们像乔治华盛顿一样从奴隶身上拔出新的牙齿，植入自己的口中。这就是作为本国根基的自由：少数人的自由，其他人的不幸。我们是自由主义者，该轮到我们做主了。
加拿大的魅力与日俱增
